# NumberInput

`TxNumberInput` wraps a native numeric input and optional step buttons. It normalizes values through `min`, `max`, and `precision`, then emits `number | null`.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/number-input/src/TxNumberInput.vue` and `number-input.test.ts`.

